dict.string: {"id":"","name":"Write a movie analysis","subtasks":[{"id":"","name":"Watch the movie","details":["Select a movie to analyze","Take notes on the plot, characters, and themes"]},{"id":"","name":"Identify key themes","details":["Analyze the underlying messages and themes in the movie","Explore the symbolic elements and motifs used to convey the themes"]},{"id":"","name":"Analyze the characters","details":["Evaluate the character development and motivations","Discuss the significance of each character in relation to the plot and themes"]},{"id":"","name":"Examine the plot structure","details":["Break down the plot into key arcs and plot points","Analyze the narrative structure and pacing of the story"]},{"id":"","name":"Evaluate filmmaking techniques","details":["Assess the use of cinematography, editing, and sound in conveying the story","Explore the visual and auditory elements that contribute to the movie's impact"]},{"id":"","name":"Discuss the impact on the audience","details":["Consider the emotional and intellectual impact on the audience","Evaluate the overall significance and relevance of the movie"]},{"id":"","name":"Write the analysis","details":["Organize the information into an analytical essay or report","Include an introduction, body paragraphs, and a conclusion"]},{"id":"","name":"Edit and refine the analysis","details":["Review and revise the analysis for clarity and coherence","Ensure the analysis effectively conveys your insights and interpretations"]},{"id":"","name":"Cite sources and references","details":["If applicable, provide citations for any external sources used in the analysis","Give credit to other critics and scholars who have contributed to your understanding"]},{"id":"","name":"Publish or present the analysis","details":["Share your analysis through a written publication, presentation, or online platform","Engage with others to discuss and exchange perspectives on the movie analysis"]}]}

{"id":"","name":"Make a salad","subtasks":[{"id":"","name":"Prepare the vegetables","details":["Wash the lettuce","Chop the cucumber","Dice the tomatoes","Slice the onion"]},{"id":"","name":"Prepare the dressing","details":["Mix olive oil and vinegar","Add salt and pepper to taste","Whisk the ingredients together"]},{"id":"","name":"Toss the salad","details":["Combine the prepared vegetables in a bowl","Drizzle the dressing over the vegetables","Gently toss the salad to coat it with the dressing"]},{"id":"","name":"Garnish the salad","details":["Add croutons for extra crunch","Sprinkle some shredded cheese on top","Garnish with fresh herbs for flavor"]},{"id":"","name":"Serve the salad","details":["Transfer the salad to a serving bowl","Serve immediately and enjoy!"]}]}
